{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce2-002-breakfast-or-lunch",
    "title": "Lesson 2: Breakfast or Lunch",
    "audioFilename": "02－Breakfast or Lunch.mp3",
    "duration": 81.345,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.24,
      "end": 1.64,
      "text": "Lesson 2.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第2课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.78,
      "end": 4.28,
      "text": "Breakfast or Lunch.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "早餐还是午餐？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.66,
      "end": 9.08,
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 10.58,
      "end": 13.74,
      "text": "Why was the writer's aunt surprised?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "作者的姑妈为什么感到惊讶？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 15.91,
      "end": 16.99,
      "text": "It was Sunday.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那天是星期日。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 17.91,
      "end": 20.89,
      "text": "I never get up early on Sundays.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "星期日我从不早起。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 21.97,
      "end": 25.63,
      "text": "I sometimes stay in bed until lunchtime.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "有时我要一直躺到吃午饭的时候。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 26.95,
      "end": 29.93,
      "text": "Last Sunday I got up very late.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "上个星期日我起得很晚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 29.93,
      "end": 32.71,
      "text": "I looked out of the window.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我望望窗外。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 33.41,
      "end": 34.91,
      "text": "It was dark outside.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "外面一片昏暗。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 35.77,
      "end": 37.37,
      "text": "What a day!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "鬼天气！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 37.91,
      "end": 38.71,
      "text": "I thought.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我想。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 39.69,
      "end": 41.19,
      "text": "It's raining again.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "又下雨了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 42.57,
      "end": 45.09,
      "text": "Just then the telephone rang.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "正在这时，电话铃响了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 45.83,
      "end": 47.57,
      "text": "It was my Aunt Lucy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是我姑妈露西打来的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 48.89,
      "end": 52.29,
      "text": "I've just arrived by train, she said.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我刚坐火车到达，”她说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 53.05,
      "end": 54.79,
      "text": "I'm coming to see you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我这就来看你。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 55.93,
      "end": 59.55,
      "text": "But I'm still having breakfast, I said.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“可我还在吃早饭，”我说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 60.35,
      "end": 61.67,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“你在干什么？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 62.43,
      "end": 62.99,
      "text": "She asked.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 63.95,
      "end": 66.55,
      "text": "I'm having breakfast, I repeated.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我在吃早饭，”我又说了一遍。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 67.73,
      "end": 69.65,
      "text": "Dear me, she said.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“天哪，”她说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 70.49,
      "end": 72.65,
      "text": "Do you always get up so late?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“你总是起得这么晚吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 73.47,
      "end": 74.51,
      "text": "It's one o'clock.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“现在已经一点钟了！”"
      }
    }
  ]
}
